     H            Y.
     F** EJKR12 *************************************
     F* B2B_S  GET PARAMETERS BY CONVERSION PROGRAM *
     F* T.SAKAKI          2016.10.18                *
     F********************************** EJKR12 *****
     FEJKPL11 IF  E           K        DISK
     I*
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140@TIME
     I                                        1   60@@TIME
     I                                        7  140@@DATE
     I*
     IINFDSP     SDS
     I                                        1  10 PGMNM
     I                                      254 263 USID
     C*
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@PGMN 10         CONV. PGM
     C* OUT
     C                     PARM           P@JYKB  2         PARTNER GROUP
     C                     PARM           P@DKBN  3         EDI DATA CODE
     C                     PARM           P@PTID 10         PARTNER ID
     C*
     C                     TIME           @TIME
     C*
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    P@JYKB
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    P@DKBN
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    P@PTID
     C*
     C           P@PGMN    CHAINEJKPL11              99
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C           DPSKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVELDPJSYS    P@JYKB
     C                     MOVELDPDKBN    P@DKBN
     C                     MOVELDPPTID    P@PTID
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
